Package: mbc-zumo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, melt
Description: Easy transcode utility, one format out
 this is a small utility used to transcode to a h264/aac stream to ingest
 into a television playout system. it will call the melt binary on the
 archive, filter it's audio level and re-encode using the x264 encoding library
